objects.subject: options
bot_text: I can inform you about : symptoms of Covid-19, vaccination for Covid-19, vaccines about Covid-19, Self-test for Covid-19, Rapid-test for Covid-19, PCR test for Covid-19, Freedom pass, Red areas in Greece, Number for EODY

objects.subject: symptoms of Covid-19
bot_text: Covid-19 have a variety of symptoms like : fever, cough, shortness of breath or difficulty breathing, Fatigue, Muscle or body aches, headache, loss of taste or smell, sore throat, vomiting and nausea.
If you thing that you have a Covid-19 symptom, please stay home and call a hospital
Calm down and call your doctor

objects.subject: vaccination for Covid-19
bot_text: With the vaccine you protect yourself and the society
The vaccine will make you strong against the virus
Vaccination will help you to keep yourself strong and healthy, you can vaccinated in the nearest vaccination center

objects.subject: vaccines about Covid-19
bot_text: The vaccines set the virus against us and for that purpose we have the following vaccines : Pfizer, Moderna and AstraZeneca

objects.subject: Self-test for Covid-19
bot_text: Self-test is an easy test to do in your home and free, all you have to do is to take the cotton swab in your nose and then put the cotton swab in the liquid of the package

objects.subject: Rapid-test for Covid-19
bot_text: Rapid test is an easy test to do in any diagnostic center, in the price of 20 euros, after you will go you will receive an email with the results

objects.subject: PCR test for Covid-19
bot_text: Pcr test it a test what you can do in a hospital, its costs 50 euros but the result it's 100% true

objects.subject: Freedom pass
user_text: Where i can find my freedom pass?
bot_text: Freedom pass is a program of government that gives 150 euro to every vaccinated human of age 18-25, for more info you can visit the website https://emvolio.gov.gr/freedompass

objects.subject: Red areas in Greece
bot_text: Red areas in Greece that is good to avoid are Crete, Santorini, Paros and Mykonos
Red areas is where the possibility to get the virus of Covid is high

objects.subject: Number for EODY
bot_text: EODY is the National Organization of Public Health
you can contact with EODY from the website https://eody.gov.gr/eody/
for details call to EODY from the phone : 210 5212000

objects.subject: Private sector
bot_text: Self tests are obligatory
The assistants of private sectors must do 2 per week
The assistants can provided self tests, one from the local pharmacy and one from the employer per week
Any assistant of private sector can take the self tests with their AMKA number
You upload your result of self tests for private sector assistant to gov.gr

objects.subject: Public service
bot_text: Self tests are obligatory
The assistants of public service must do 1 per week
The assistants can provided self test, one from the local pharmacy
Any assistnat of public service can take the self test with their AMKA number
You upload your result of self test for public service assistant to gov.gr
